WEBVTT

00:00.190 --> 00:01.524
Previously on "Manhattan"...

00:01.559 --> 00:03.372
You've got a nuclear
physicist carrying your water?

00:03.372 --> 00:04.688
Dr. Theodore Sinclair.

00:04.721 --> 00:06.321
We had no idea you were a physicist.

00:06.355 --> 00:08.617
Let me guess, something's
recapturing neutrons.

00:08.652 --> 00:11.655
Reactor fuel. What if
reactor plutonium isn't pure?

00:11.689 --> 00:13.088
Frank always assumes the worst.

00:13.122 --> 00:14.711
You were married when I met you.

00:14.736 --> 00:17.903
He wanted to start a
new life. He was naive.

00:17.951 --> 00:19.890
What did you do at work
today? Trick question.

00:19.925 --> 00:22.241
If somebody asked that on
the phone, I'd have to cut in.

00:22.734 --> 00:24.330
Let us play.

00:24.909 --> 00:27.248
You want me to sleep
with... they're all whores?

00:27.282 --> 00:29.383
It's $2.50 for last night.

00:29.418 --> 00:33.564
So what happens now? We go
back to being sworn enemies?

00:33.598 --> 00:36.640
Well, as long as we're both
stranded, how about a drop to drink?

00:36.675 --> 00:38.725
Or we could skip the drink.

00:38.919 --> 00:41.567
- I have to go back to the office.
- What's wrong?

00:41.997 --> 00:43.550
I don't know yet.

